Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:01:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru's attacks mercilessly\Nrained down on all of Skypiea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is an eyesore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people, the trees, the land!\NReturn to where you belong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let everything rain into the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Island won't last much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no safe havens left on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Robin and Usopp's\Ngroup was still beneath Giant Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's far above now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time until\Nhis ship reaches the top of the vine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it Eneru wants there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gold bell at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need for good\Nold God's Shrine either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor for the city of Shandora below it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is but one thing left\Nin this land that I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The golden grand belfry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Luffy, in an attempt to\Ncatch Eneru, rushed up Giant Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't let you have\Nthe golden bell, Eneru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Angel Island Obliterated!\NThe Horror of the Raigo's Advent!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gold bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wyper...\N--Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What're you guys talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also spoke of the bell before\Nbeing hit by Eneru's electric attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's going after it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where exactly is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait! This is no time for that!\NYou saw that thunderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna die if we don't get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere near the top of this giant vine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?! How do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We promised we'd wait\Nfor Nami back on our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gonna be back with Luffy any time now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruins of Shandora in the layer below us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This vine pierces right through\Nthe very center of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno if it's ruins or what,\Nbut it's been blasted to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could be next, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A map I found in the ruins\Nindicated that the grand belfry
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that held the golden bell was\Nlocated in the city's center.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you completely ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the shock from\Nbeing thrust upward by the vine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,might have thrown the bell\Neven further skyward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's directly above here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The singing voice of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold has a huge bell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. I'm above Giant Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt anyone would come\Nsearching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in these skies above God's Shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after 400 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. Where is the golden bell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm astonished he made it here\Nwith that weight attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right there! Eneru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper! What are you planning to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're gonna climb the vine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Get away from the vine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tip of the vine?! What happened above?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:08:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Don't tell me\NLuffy and Nami fell with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You can't in your condition!\NYou're all beat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if you do climb up, there's\Nno way to reach Eneru in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's directly above!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bell that Great Warrior Calgara sought!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calgara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what our true goal is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru! I refuse to let you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you intend to\Nclimb up here in that state?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there for a while. I'll show\Nyou something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! I gotta figure\Nsomething out while he's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my only choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:10:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Yo-Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.78,0:10:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm back on track!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance to get on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! I finally caught up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Nami! What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun and Usopp saved me,\Nso I was down below!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! You were?! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thunderclouds... are changing shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The sky!\N--Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is bad! Save us!\N--The sky's pitch dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's happening?!\N--Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Into the ocean! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a giant ball floating in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's bad news...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a thundercloud\Nwrapped in a spherical shroud...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it's packed with intense currents\Nand internal electric discharges!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's directly above Angel Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thunderclouds turned spherical...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:12:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is a nightmare! This isn't\Nsomething you see in real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What more is he planning to unleash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry! Into the ocean!\N--Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you will learn that the heavens are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Maxim and my power,\NI can accomplish such acts of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Look at that!\N--It's falling onto Angel Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's too late!\N--We're not going to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Run! Hurry!\N--I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the White Berets manage to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The White Berets saved us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:14:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The island we were born on and our\Nhometown are completely gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Sea Clouds were obliterated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how the sky should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the thunderbolts are still raining down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get the feeling\NI'll be leaving alive now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He eradicated Angel Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:15:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so ruthless, Eneru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What loud rumbling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to wait. We have to\Ntake them back to the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Get on, so we can go back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's headed for our ship!\NWe gotta get going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't? Why not?!\NWhat're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't have to save you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I still have unfinished business here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfinished business? What could\Nyou possibly have left to do here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to get back\Nat Eneru or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a gold bell up above!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold? Your life is more important,\Nyou know! Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if lightning doesn't hurt you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:16:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he has the power to destroy\Neverything in other ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's gold you want, then look!\NYou have some on your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about some gold bell! You'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you quit it, already?! You--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold... it existed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old diamond-head's ancestor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it exists, that's fine. If not, that's fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really out to prove\Nhis innocence or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a duel with the man\Nwho screwed up my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to let the old guy\Nand the others below know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the city of gold was in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ring the bell...\Nthey should be able to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, they'll keep on searching\Nthe ocean floor until they die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let Eneru take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the huge bell can\Nbe heard from anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so that's why I'm going to ring the gold bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The City of Gold has a huge bell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Noland's logbook did mention it had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why do you ask?\N--Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought up a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we rang that huge bell,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you think old diamond-head\Nand the monkeys below would hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd hear it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he says he's gonna\Ndo something, he means it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did say that. But given the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to ring the bell, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Even if Nami tries to\Nbring him back, he won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's after the same thing Eneru is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission to board this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! I told you it was a bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Did you see the silly\Nlittle island vanish from the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl. I assume you're not\Ngoing to try and sweet-talk me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by asking me to take you\Nto Endless Vearth again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I have what I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy all of Skypiea\Nwith this next Raigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can be allowed to escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Including the several unmoving\Nvoices directly below you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Directly below?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to eradicate this land\Nthat is out of place in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and change everything\Nback to how it should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my duty as God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, rubber man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look on wistfully and\Nwait until the end arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! We will send you\Ninto the sky, without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will ring that bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling lonely, talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gaze at the heavens\Nas you wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the moon,\Nyou keep your gaze constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your deep reflection wanes\Nas you slowly disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are, let those words guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream, you travelers who spend\Ncountless nights drifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you may not be able to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely start moving forward again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the power of the Raigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up are the cumuloregalis\Nclouds themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.75,0:23:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything we can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's important that we, the inheritors\Nof Calgara's wishes, ring that bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock over this vine?! Am I our\Nlast line of defense after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Guarantee me I'll survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Knock Over Giant Jack!\NLast Hope for Escape"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
